instructions: Place the plate in the center of the Charger
Place the napkin on the center of the plate
Place the Dinner Fork immediately left of the Charger
Place the Salad Fork immediately to the left of the Dinner Fork
Place the Dinner Knife immediately to the right of the Charger
Place the Tea Spoon immediately to the right of the Dinner Knife
Place the Soup Spoon immediately to the right of the Tea Spoon
Place the Water Glass to the right of the Charger and above the Dinner Knife
Place the Wine Glass immediately to the right of the Water Glass
Place the second Wine Glass between the 1st Wine Glass and the Tea Spoon
Place the Coffee Cup to the right of the 2nd Wine Glass
Place the Bread Plate to the left of the Charger and directly above the forks.
Place the Butter Knife in the center of the Bread Plate with handle pointing toward the Water Glass
Place the Dessert Fork above the Charger with the handle pointing toward the Bread Plate
Place the Dessert Spoon below the Dessert Fork with the handle pointing toward the Water Glass
